title: BRIEF-Collplant Petitions Court To Voluntarily Delist Ordinary Shares From The Tel Aviv Stock Exchange
text:
April 16, 2018 / 10:51 AM / Updated 11 minutes ago BRIEF-Collplant Petitions Court To Voluntarily Delist Ordinary Shares From The Tel Aviv Stock Exchange Reuters Staff 
April 16 (Reuters) - Collplant Holdings Ltd: 
* COLLPLANT PETITIONS COURT TO VOLUNTARILY DELIST ORDINARY SHARES FROM THE TEL AVIV STOCK EXCHANGE 
* COLLPLANT HOLDINGS LTD - DELISTING FROM THE TASE IS THE NEXT STEP IN CO'S DEVELOPMENT AS "THE COMPANY BECOMES MORE US FACING" Source text ( bit.ly/2H3TcvL ) Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
